.98%20beat%20estimates%20by%20%240.07%2C%20and%20revenue%20of%20%2432%20billion%20topped%20estimates%20by%20nearly%20%241%20billion%20while%20representing%20year-over-year%20growth%20of%2011%25.%20Across%20all%20of%20its%20products%2C%20Meta%20reported%20a%20record%203.88%20billion%20monthly%20active%20users%20in%20the%20month%20of%20June%2C%20representing%20year-over-year%20growth%20of%206%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20significant%20rebound%20in%20advertising%20revenue%2C%20combined%20with%20the%20company's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-meta-efficiency-facebook-apple-amazon-earnings-2023-2%23%3A~%3Atext%3DEnter%2520Mark%2520Zuckerberg%252C%2520CEO%2520of%2Cthis%2520means%2520for%2520Big%2520Tech.%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Byear%20of%20efficiency%26quot%3B%20cost%20cuts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20helped%20drive%20the%20better-than-expected%20earnings%20results.%20And%20Zuckerberg%20expects%20those%20tailwinds%20to%20continue%2C%20with%20Meta%20offering%20solid%20third-quarter%20revenue%20guidance%20of%20%2432%20billion%20to%20%2434.5%20billion%2C%20well%20ahead%20of%20estimates%20of%20%2431.1%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple's%20iOS%20privacy%20change%20in%202021%20made%20it%20difficult%20for%20social-media%20companies%20to%20track%20users%2C%20weighing%20on%20ad%20revenue.%20But%20Meta%20revenue%20has%20been%20recovering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZuckerberg%20also%20highlighted%20Meta's%20new%20product%20launches%20that%20are%20resonating%20with%20its%20customers%2C%20including%20continued%20growth%20in%20its%20TikTok%20competitor%20Reels%2C%20and%20its%20recent%20launch%20of%20Twitter%20competitor%20Threads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20the%20most%20exciting%20roadmap%20I've%20seen%20in%20a%20while%20with%20Llama%202%2C%20Threads%2C%20Reels%2C%20new%20AI%20products%20in%20the%20pipeline%2C%20and%20the%20launch%20of%20Quest%203%20this%20fall%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20Threads%2C%20he%20said%20the%20compan