20associated%20with%20the%20BJP.%20The%20perception%20that%20the%20party%20used%20its%20money%20power%20to%20topple%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20government%20in%20Maharashtra%20has%20gained%20ground%20all%20across%20the%20country.%20What%20has%20strengthened%20the%20perception%20is%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20declaration%20of%20the%20events%20that%20led%20to%20the%20Thackeray%E2%80%99s%20downfall%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-shiv-sena-uddhav-thackeray-eknath-shinde%5C%22%3Eillegal%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%20But%20even%20after%20the%20apex%20court%E2%80%99s%20ruling%2C%20the%20BJP%20executed%20a%20split%20in%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20%E2%80%93%20bringing%20Ajit%20Pawar%20and%20eight%20of%20his%20colleagues%20to%20join%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20cabinet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20initially%20bracketed%20the%20opposition%20leaders%20who%20are%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgroup%20of%20corrupt%20leaders%E2%80%9D%20who%20are%20under%20the%20scanner%20of%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%2C%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20and%20Income%20Tax.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20has%20far%20more%20corrupt%20leaders%20from%20east%20to%20west%20and%20from%20north%20to%20south.%20They%20were%20under%20the%20scanner%20of%20the%20central%20agencies%20for%20corruption.%20After%20joining%20the%20BJP%2C%20they%20stand%20cleaned%20in%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20washing%20machine%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20spokesman%2C%20Manoj%20Jha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20said%20to%20be%20apprehensive%20because%20it%20had%20come%20to%20power%20in%202014%20after%20heaping%20charges%20of%20corruption%20and%20%E2%80%98policy%20paralysis%E2%80%99%20on%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20government.%20Now%2C%20the%20charges%20of%20incompetence%20and%20corruption%20against%20it%20%E2%80%93%20coupled%20with%20an%20organised%20opposition%20%E2%80%93%20ca