20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20launched%20a%20virtual%20walkthrough%20of%20the%20upcoming%20museum%20after%20inaugurating%20a%20three-day%20International%20Museum%20Expo%20at%20Pragati%20Maidan%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%20evening%2C%20PM%20Modi%20inaugurated%20the%20International%20Exhibition-cum-Convention%20Centre%20(IECC)%20complex%2C%20developed%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20about%20Rs%202%2C700%20crore%20with%20a%20campus%20area%20of%20approximately%20123%20acres%2C%20and%20unveiled%20its%20new%20name%20-%20Bharat%20Mandapam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20address%20at%20the%20inauguration%2C%20PM%20Modi%20also%20announced%20Yuge%20Yugeen%20Bharat%20National%20Museum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20museum%20will%20have%20%26quot%3Beight%20thematic%20segments%26quot%3B%20and%20will%20showcase%20the%20rich%20civilisational%20culture%20of%20India%20spanning%20over%205%2C000%20years%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20segments%20broadly%20include%20ancient%20Indian%20knowledge%2C%20ancient%20to%20medieval%2C%20medieval%2C%20medieval%20to%20transition%20phase%2C%20modern%20India%2C%20the%20colonial%20rule%20(when%20the%20Dutch%2C%20the%20British%2C%20the%20Portuguese%20and%20others%20came%20to%20India)%2C%20the%20freedom%20struggle%20and%20the%20100%20years%20from%201947%20onwards%2Cincluding%20the%20vision%20ahead%2C%20the%20senior%20official%20told%20PTI.%20It%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bforward-looking%20museum%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20virtual%20walkthrough%20of%20the%20museum%20provides%20a%20digital%20experience%20into%20how%20the%20galleries%20and%20gardens%20in%20it%20will%20appear%20once%20the%20museum%20is%20completed.%20It%20showed%20that%20the%20galleries%20through%20exhibits%20will%20inform%20the%20visitor%20about%20ancient%20town%20planning%20systems%2C%20the%20Vedas%2C%20Upanishads%2C%20ancient%20medical%20knowledge%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMauryan%20to%20Gupta%20Empires%2C%20Vijayanagara%20Empire%2C%20M