r%20the%20Centre%2C%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%20argued%20that%20the%20circumstances%20of%20Mr%20Mishra%20are%20unusual%20in%20view%20of%20the%20coming%20review%20by%20the%20global%20terror%20financing%20watchdog%20FATF%20(Financial%20Action%20Task%20Force).%20The%20onsite%20review%20of%20India's%20regulations%20and%20supervision%20by%20the%20inter-governmental%20organisation%2C%20which%20also%20combats%20combat%20money%20laundering%2C%20is%20due%20in%20November.%20The%20team%20is%20likely%20to%20reach%20on%20November%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAre%20you%20saying%20all%20other%20officers%20are%20incompetent%3F%20Only%20one%20officer%20can%20do%3F%26quot%3B%20shot%20back%20the%20bench%20of%20Justices%20BR%20Gavai%2C%20Justice%20Vikram%20Nath%20and%20Justice%20Sanjay%20Karol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20officer%20is%20indispensable.%20There%20is%20a%20leadership%20is%20every%20organization%20but%20there%20has%20to%20be%20a%20continuity%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Centre%20responded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20pointed%20out%20that%20even%20after%20holding%20his%20extensions%20since%202021%20illegal%2C%20the%20Centre%20has%20been%20given%20time%20till%20July%2031.%20When%20the%20Centre%20persisted%20with%20its%20arguments%2C%20Senior%20advocate%20Abhishek%20Singhvi%2C%20who%20represented%20the%20petitioners%2C%20said%20the%20FATF%20review%20is%20a%20process%20involving%2040%20parameters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMoney%20laundering%20is%20one%20such%20parameter.%20Also%2C%20the%20FATF%20review%20is%20an%20ongoing%20process%20till%202024.%20So%2C%20will%20they%20then%20seek%20extension%20till%202024%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOut%20of%20140%20crore%20people%2C%20are%20we%20depending%20on%20only%20one%20officer%3F%20The%20conduct%20of%20Centre%20seeking%20extension%20is%20deplorable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20has%20cited%20the%20peer%20review%20every%20time%20it%20extended%20Mr%20Mishra's%20term.%20The%20officer%20was%20given%20charge%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20November%202018%20and%20was%20to%20retire%20in%20two%20years%20when%20turned%2060.%20But%20in%20November%202020%2C%20he%20got%20one%20extension%2C%20and%20it%20was%20followed%20by%20two%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20the%20Centre%20had%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20he%20would%20retire%20in%20November%20and%20that%20the%20petition%20challenging%20his%20extension%20was%20meant%20to%20appease%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20masters%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Congress%20leader%20Randeep%20Surjewala%2C%20who%20has%20filed%20one%20of%20the%20petitions%2C%20has%20claimed%20that%20the%20government%20is%20misusing%20central%20agencies%20to%20target%20the%20opposition%20leaders%20and%20destabilise%20elected%20governments%20in%20non-BJP-ruled%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690459560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F2u5oqk7o_sanjay-kumar-mishra-ndtv-650-_650x400_11_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fenforcement-directorate-chief-can-stay-till-september-15-supreme-court-4245148%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Enforcement%20Directorate%20Chief%20Can%20Stay%20Till%20September%2015%3A%20Supreme%20Court%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fenforcement-directorate-chief-can-stay-till-september-15-supreme-court-4245148%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fenforcement-directorate-chief-can-stay-till-september-15-supreme-court-4245148%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fenforcement-directorate-chief-can-stay-till-september-15-supreme-court-4245148%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Venice%20Days%20Title%20%E2%80%98The%20Zola%20Experience%2C%E2%80%99%20Centered%20on%20Stage%20Production%20