C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frssharma3%2Fstatus%2F1484584060697845763%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estate-of-the-art%20security%20infrastructure%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20has%20never%20faced%20a%20security%20breach.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20own%20personal%20data%20was%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fanivar%2Fstatus%2F1668077292718010368%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexposed%20in%20a%20massive%20leak%20of%20CoWIN%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0via%20the%20Telegram%20app.%20Officials%20first%20denied%20a%20breach%20had%20taken%20place%2C%20then%20days%20later%2C%20Delhi%20police%20said%20they%20had%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fcowin-data-leak-bihar-arrest-telegram-8679180%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earrested%20two%20individuals%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20relation%20to%20the%20leak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20leak%20%E2%80%93%20including%20names%2C%20Aadhaar%20national%20IDs%2C%20mobile%20numbers%2C%20voter%20IDs%2C%20passports%20and%20COVID%20vaccination%20status%20of%20millions%20of%20individuals%20%E2%80%93%20was%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20in%20India%2C%20and%20came%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20other%20breaches%20of%20CoWIN%20and%20Aadhaar%20data%2C%20and%20the%20records%20of%20a%20leading%20hospital%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20breaches%20of%20health%20data%20are%20particularly%20concerning%2C%20digital%20experts%20said%2C%20as%20they%20leave%20individuals%20vulnerable%20to%20scams%2C%20harassment%20and%20discrimination%20without%20remedy%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20data%20protection%20law%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20warned%20it%20also%20undermines%20India%E2%80%99s%20aim%20to%20develop%20and%20export%20to%20Asian%20and%20African%20countries%20its%20digital%20public%20infrastructure%20model%20comprising%20Aadhaar%2C%20mobile%20payment%20system%20UPI%20and%20the%20National%20Health%20Stack%20data%20platform%2C%20that%20authorities%20say%20will%20improve%20access%20and%20efficiency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20pushing%20its%20digital%20public%20infrastructure%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20putting%20people%20at%20risk%20from%20data%20collection%20and%20data%20overreach%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Raman%20Jit%20Singh%20Chima%2C%20Asia%20policy%20director%20at%20digital%20rights%20group%20Access%20Now.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20bad%20model.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20push%20for%20greater%20digitisation%20of%20health%20data%20is%20happening%20without%20discussion%20or%20adequate%20data%20protection.%20India%20is%20seeing%20an%20increase%20in%20cyberattacks%2C%20and%20the%20refusal%20to%20acknowledge%20breaches%20and%20to%20hold%20institutions%20accountable%20is%20a%20reckless%20approach%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20of%20electronics%20and%20information%20technology%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20health%20ministry%2C%20in%20a%20June%2012%20statement%2C%20said%20that%20the%20CoWIN%20portal%20%E2%80%9Cis%20completely%20safe%20with%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1931691%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadequate%20safeguards%20for%20data%20privacy%3C%2Fa%3E.%20All%20steps%20have%20been%20taken%20and%20are%20being%20taken%20to%20ensure%20security%20of%20the%20data.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20federal%20Computer%20Emergency%20Response%20Team%20was%20investigating%20the%20incident%2C%20it%20added.%20No%20details%20have%20since%20been%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJunior%20IT%20minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20said%20at%20the%20time%20that%20the%20leaked%20CoWIN%20data%20was%20accessed%20by%20a%20bot%20%E2%80%9Cfrom%20a%20threat%20actor%20database%2C%20which%20seems%20to%20have%20been%20populated%20with%20previously%20breached%2Fstolen%20data.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20does%20not%20appear%20that%20CoWIN%20app%20or%20database%20has%20been%20directly%20breached%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20on%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHighly%20sensitive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20ambitious%20Digital%20India%20programme%2C%20there%20is%20increasing%20digitisation%20of%20data%20and%20services%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20national%20digital%20health%20mission%20that%20aims%20to%20link%20individual%20health%20records%20to%20a%20unique%20ID%20similar%20to%20the%20Aadhaar%20ID%2C%20has%20raised%20concerns%20about%20data%20security%20and%20the%20potential%20for%20misuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20rush%20to%20build%20out%20the%20digital%20public%20infrastructure%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20very%20suitability%20of%20these%20technologies%20has%20gone%20unchallenged%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Aarushi%20Gupta%20at%20Digital%20Futures%20Lab%2C%20a%20research%20collective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGiven%20the%20vast%20amounts%20of%20data%20collection%2C%20processing%2C%20and%20exchange%20%E2%80%A6%20citizens%20are%20at%20considerable%20risk%20of%20their%20data%20being%20leaked%20and%20their%20privacy%20rights%20being%20compromised%2C%20as%20seen%20with%20the%20recent%20leak%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20was%20the%20biggest%20target%20for%20cyberattacks%20after%20the%20United%20States%20in%202021%20and%202022%2C%20with%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cloudsek.com%2Fthreatintelligence%2Fcowin-data-leak-claim-and-cloudsek-analysis%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enearly%20500%20attacks%20last%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20increase%20of%20nearly%20a%20fourth%2C%20according%20to%20cybersecurity%20firm%20CloudSEK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20separate%20study%20by%20NordV