0with%20%24282.7%20million%20in%20gross%20billings%20in%20the%20three%20months%20to%20June%2030%2C%20just%20a%207%25%20decline%20from%20the%20same%20period%20the%20prior%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMattel%20said%20that%20despite%20gross%20billings%20for%20Barbie%20falling%2C%20sales%20for%20its%20Disney%20Princess%2C%20Disney%20Frozen%2C%20and%20Monster%20High%20franchises%20helped%20boost%20its%20dolls%20category%20overall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECFO%20Anthony%20DiSilvestro%20said%20at%20the%20company's%20earnings%20call%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20Barbie's%20POS%2C%20which%20is%20the%20sales%20actually%20made%20by%20retailers%2C%20was%20down%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Blow-double%20digits%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20year%2C%20but%20that%20so%20far%20in%20July%20it%20had%20turned%20positive.%20DiSilvestro%20said%20this%20was%20down%20to%20promotions%20being%20shifted%20to%20the%20second%20half%20of%20the%20year%20to%20better%20align%20with%20the%20movie's%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMattel%20execs%20spoke%20about%20how%20the%20movie%20had%20ultimately%20catapulted%20the%20doll%20into%20the%20spotlight%2C%20given%20the%20company%20the%20chance%20to%20collaborate%20with%20other%20brands%2C%20and%20created%20a%20%26quot%3Bhalo%20effect%26quot%3B%20for%20Barbie%2C%20with%20the%20impact%20on%20sales%20expected%20to%20last%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECEO%20Ynon%20Kreiz%20said%20that%20Barbie's%20range%20of%20movie-related%20toys%20and%20products%20had%20sold%20out%20%26quot%3Bvery%20fast%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20more%20items%20would%20continue%20to%20be%20released.%20Mattel%20said%20that%20as%20well%20as%20releasing%20a%20soundtrack%2C%20it%20had%20entered%20into%20more%20than%20165%20consumer%20product%20partnerships%20tied%20to%20the%20movie%2C%20with%20thousands%20of%20displays%20in%20stores%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20success%20of%20the%20Barbie%20movie%20is%20a%20milestone%20moment%20for%20Mattel%20and%20it%20really%20is%20a%20showcase%20for%20the%20cultural%20resonance%20of%20the%20brand%2C%26quot%3B%20COO%20Richard%20Dickson%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20we've%20seen%2C%20the%20success%20is%20far%20beyond%20the%20film.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20all%20see%20the%20world%20is%20playing%20with%20Barbie%2C%20whether%20it's%20our%20toys%2C%20fashion%2C%20accessories%2C%20or%20content%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20brand%20has%20reached%20a%20new%20level%20of%20cultural%20relevance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20a%20week%20from%20its%20global%20release%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fbox-office-records-barbenheimer-broke-2023-7%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BBarbie%26quot%3B%20has%20already%20smashed%20a%20number%20of%20box-office%20records%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20had%20the%20largest%20opening%20weekend%20at%20the%20domestic%20box%20office%20so%20far%20this%20year%2C%20bringing%20in%20%24162%20million%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20further%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdeadline.com%2F2023%2F07%2Fbarbie-oppenheimer-barbenheimer-christopher-nolan-cillian-murphy-margot-robbie-ryan-gosling-gloabl-international-box-office-1235443180%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24194%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%20internationally.%20It%20was%20also%20the%20largest%20opening%20weekend%20ever%20for%20a%20female%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbarbie-mattel-doll-sales-dropping-despite-greta-gerwig-movie-mania-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690458969000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c25330101bd0001929c1f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbarbie-mattel-doll-sales-dropping-despite-greta-gerwig-movie-mania-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sales%20of%20Barbie%20dolls%20and%20merchandise%20fell%20yea