%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk's%20'X'%20Temporarily%20Banned%20In%20Indonesia.%20Here's%20Why%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk's%20X%2C%20the%20social%20media%20site%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter%2C%20has%20hit%20a%20roadblock%20in%20Indonesia.%20The%20social%20media%20site%20was%20blocked%20in%20Indonesia%20for%20violating%20local%20pornography%20and%20gambling%20laws%2C%20reported%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Feconomy%2F2023%2F7%2F26%2Felon-musks-x-com-blocked-in-indonesia-under-curbs-on-porn%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAl%20Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndonesia's%20Ministry%20of%20Communication%20and%20Informatics%20in%20a%20statement%20said%20that%20the%20site%20was%20restricted%20as%20the%20domain%20had%20been%20previously%20used%20by%20sites%20that%20did%20not%20adhere%20to%20the%20country's%20strict%20laws%20against%20%26quot%3Bnegative%26quot%3B%20content%20such%20as%20pornography%20and%20gambling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20media%20outlet%20reported%20that%20executives%20from%20X%20are%20already%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20ministry%20to%20solve%20the%20issue.%20It%20was%20reported%20that%20they%20are%20going%20to%20send%20officials%20a%20letter%20stating%20Twitter%20now%20owns%20the%20X.com%20domain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsman%20Kansong%2C%20the%20director%20general%20of%20information%20and%20public%20communication%20at%20the%20ministry%20told%20local%20media%2C%20%26quot%3BEarlier%20today%2C%20we%20spoke%20with%20representatives%20from%20Twitter%20and%20they%20will%20send%20a%20letter%20to%20us%20to%20say%20that%20X.com%20will%20be%20used%20by%20Twitter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20that%20Indonesians%20cannot%20access%20the%20platform%20currently.%20Indonesia%20alone%20has%20about%2024%20million%20users%20on%20the%20microblogging%20media%20site.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Elon%20Musk%20dropped%20a%20bombshell%20on%20Monday%20that%20he%20will%20be%20changing%20Twitter's%20name%