a%20Muharram%20procession%20on%20a%20traditional%20route%20in%20Srinagar%20passing%20through%20the%20Lal%20Chowk%20area%2C%20with%20hundreds%20of%20people%20participating%20in%20it%20amid%20tight%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%20had%20on%20Wednesday%20permitted%20a%20two-hour%20window%20-%20from%206%20am%20to%208%20am%20-%20for%20the%20procession.%20Mourners%20filled%20the%20streets%20as%20they%20peacefully%20marched%20on%20the%20Gurubazaar%20to%20Dalgate%20route%20carrying%20flags%20and%20chanting%20in%20unison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20dividend%20of%20peace%2C%26quot%3B%20Srinagar%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20Aijaz%20Asad%20said%2C%20thanking%20security%20agencies%20as%20well%20as%20local%20volunteers%20for%20their%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20had%20assembled%20at%20Gurubazaar%20around%205.30%20am%20for%20the%208th%20Day%20procession%20and%20many%20hoped%20that%20the%20administration%20will%20now%20allow%20the%20important%2010th%20Day%20march%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELieutenant%20Governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%20said%20the%20street%20violence%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20has%20ended%20and%20an%20era%20of%20peace%20has%20dawned%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory%20as%20he%20expressed%20satisfaction%20over%20the%20holding%20of%20Muharram%20procession.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20happy%20to%20tell%20you%20that%20today%20the%208th%20of%20the%20Muharram%20procession%20was%20taken%20out%20after%20decades%20and%20concluded%20in%20Srinagar%20peacefully.%20It%20would%20be%20wrong%20to%20do%20any%20politics%20on%20religious%20events%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20while%20addressing%20a%20conference%20on%20Sufism%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%2C%20Kashmir%2C%20Vijay%20Kumar%20told%20reporters%20that%20a%20three-tier%20security%20arrangement%20has%20been%20provided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20in%20more%20than%2030%20years%20that%20the%20procession%