Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fs%26amp%3Bp_500%3Futm_medium%3Dingest%26utm_source%3Dmarkets%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20overbought.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks-priciest-in-20-years-vs-bonds-expect-weak-returns-for-years-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690458150000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c143d81e871c00191afe0f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstocks-priciest-in-20-years-vs-bonds-expect-weak-returns-for-years-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20growing%20chorus%20of%20experts%20are%20now%20pointing%20out%20that%20equity%20valuations%20are%20now%20looking%20increasingly%20stretched%2C%20raising%20the%20risk%20of%20a%20correction.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jwilkins%40insider.com%20(Joseph%20Wilkins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstocks-priciest-in-20-years-vs-bonds-expect-weak-returns-for-years-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Survey%20At%20Gyanvapi%20Mosque%20Till%20High%20Court%20Decision%20On%20August%203%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20will%20be%20no%20survey%20at%20Varanasi's%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20till%20August%203%2C%20when%20the%20final%20order%20on%20the%20matter%20will%20be%20given%2C%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20said%20today%20while%20hearing%20a%20plea%20challenging%20a%20district%20court's%20order%20for%20a%20survey.%20The%20High%20Court%20reserved%20its%20order%20after%20long%20arguments%20over%20the%20need%20for%20a%20survey%20by%20the%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%2C%20which%20has%20been%20a%20demand%20of%20the%20Hindu%20petitioners%2C%20who%20argue%20that%20the%20mosque%20stands%20on%20the%20remains%20of%20a%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ASI%20survey%20is%20necessary%20because%20Anjuman%20Masjid%20(Anjuman%20Intezamia%20Masjid%2C%20which%20manages%20the%20mosque)%20has%20said%20the%20structure%20in%20question%20(the%20temple)%20is%20based%20on%20imagination%20and%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20ground%20reality.%20They%20say%20the%20mosque%20was%20never%20in%20possession%20of%20anyone%20else%20except%20Muslims%20since%20its%20inception%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20lawyer%20for%20one%20of%20the%20petitioners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20research%20work%20of%20Neil%20G%2C%20who%20worked%20for%201975%20to%201990%2C%20and%20I%20have%20photos%20which%20show%20disputed%20structure%2C%26quot%3B%20argued%20another%20petitioner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20court%20said%20a%20decision%20on%20evidence%20is%20not%20necessary%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20the%20Hindu%20group%20argued%20that%20a%20survey%20is%20needed%20for%20the%20disposal%20of%20the%20main%20suit%20--%20which%20is%20a%20demand%20to%20perform%20puja%20at%20the%20site%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20suit%20is%20pending%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20had%20put%20a%20freeze%20on%20the%20survey%2C%20which%20expired%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20has%20already%20said%20that%20if%20devotees%20like%20us%20can%20perform%20puja%20on%20one%20day%2C%20how%20can%20making%20it%20a%20daily%20or%20weekly%20affair%20lead%20to%20conversion%20of%20the%20character%20of%20the%20mosque%3F%C2%A0%20For%20the%20disposal%20of%20suit%2C%20a%20survey%20is%20required%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawyer%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepresenting%20the%20mosque%20committee%2C%20senior%20advocate%20SFA%20Naqvi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20tried%20their%20level%20best%20to%20say%20that%20no%20digging%20is%20being%20done%2C%20but%20we%20have%20annexed%20photos%20where%20they%20have%20used%20spades.%20They%20reached%20there%20with%20these%20instruments%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20someone%20comes%20into%20court%20with%20a%20weapon%2C%20it%20doesn't%20mean%20he%20will%20use%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chief%20Justice%20Pritinker%20Diwaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20put%20the%20survey%20on%20hold%20yesterday%20over%20doubts%20about%20the%20process%2C%20especially%20after%20the%20lawyer%20for%20the%20Hindu%20group%20pointed%20out%20that%20at%20a%20later%20stage%20in%20the%20survey%2C%20excavation%20under%20the%20structure%20of%20the%20mosque%20might%20be%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mosque%20committee%20has%20argued%20that%20the%20structure%20is%20over%20a%20thousand%20years%20old%20and%20any%20digging%20might%20destabilise%20it%20and%20it%20can%20collapse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20demand%20for%20a%20scientific%20survey%20sharpened%20after%20on%20a%20purported%20'Shivling'%20was%20found%20during%20a%20video%20survey%20carried%20out%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20complex%20on%20orders%20of%20a%20lower%20court.%20The%20Hindu%20side%20has%20claimed%20that%20a%20temple%20built%20at%20the%20site%20in%201585%20on%20the%20orders%20of%20Raja%20Todar%20Mal%20--%20a%20minister%20of%20Emperor%20Akbar%20--%20was%20demolished%20in%201669.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mosque%20committee%20has%20objected%20to%20a%20scientific%20investigation%2C%20arguing%20that%20the%20case%20is%20about%20worshipping%20at%20a%20shrine%20inside%20the%20complex%20and%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20its%20structure.%20The%20object%20being%20called%20a%20%26quot%3BShivling%26quot%3B%20is%20actually%20a%20%26quot%3Bfountain%26quot%3B%2C%20they%20have%20contended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%2C%20located%20next%20to%20Varanasi's%20iconic%20Vishwanath%20temple%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20several%20mosques%20that%20Hindu%20hardliners%20believe%20were%20built%20on%20the%20ruins%20of%20temples.%20It%20was%20one%20of%20the%20three%20temple-mosque%20rows%2C%20besides%20Ayodhya%20and%20Mathura%2C%20which%20the%20BJP%20raised