2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20late%201960s%20of%20the%20last%20century%2C%20Mordechai%20Yona%20founded%20the%20group%20of%20companies%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Heftziba%C2%A0%20Group%E2%80%99%20whose%20business%20was%20in%20the%20field%20of%20construction%20and%20over%20the%20years%20his%20son%2C%20Boaz%20Yona%2C%20joined%20him%20in%20managing%20the%20group%E2%80%99s%20business.%20Later%2C%20the%20Heftziva%20Group%20became%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20residential%20construction%20companies%20in%20Israel%2C%20selling%20thousands%20of%20apartments%20to%20many%20families%E2%80%A6%20In%20August%202007%2C%20the%20group%20collapsed%2C%20and%20liquidation%20proceedings%20began%20against%20it%2C%20while%20its%20financial%20debts%20amounted%20to%20approximately%201.5%20billion%20shekels.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20collapse%20of%20the%20group%20caused%20a%20severe%20blow%20to%20buyers%20who%20were%20left%20without%20apartments%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20were%20not%20even%20given%20guarantees%20against%20the%20amounts%20they%20paid%20%E2%80%93%20contrary%20to%20the%20law.%20Boaz%20Yona%2C%20who%20served%20at%20the%20time%20as%20a%20director%20of%20the%20Heftziba%20Group%2C%20was%20convicted%20(as%20part%20of%20a%20plea%20deal)%20of%20having%20used%20the%20apartments%20buyers%E2%80%99%20money%20for%20his%20personal%20needs%2C%20refrained%20from%20providing%20them%20with%20legal%20guarantees%20to%20secure%20their%20investments%20in%20the%20apartments%2C%20and%20kept%20false%20records%20in%20the%20company%20books.%20He%20was%20sentenced%20for%20seven%20years%20in%20prison%20and%20was%20ordered%20to%20compensate%20the%20apartment%20buyers%20in%20the%20amount%20of%20NIS%20%5BIsraeli%20New%20Shekel%5D%204%20million.%20A%20short%20time%20before%2C%20in%20May%202011%2C%20Mordechai%20Yona%20passed%20away.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20in%20the%20public%20in%20Israel%2C%20and%20especially%20the%20victims%20of%20the%20Heftziba%20company%2C%20asked%20how%20the%20regulators%20and%20state%20authorities%20were%20asleep%20when%20concerns%20were%20raised%20about%20the%20company.%20The%20answer%20to%20that%20lies%2C%20perhaps%2C%20in%20Liberia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20ministry%20cables%20published%20in%20April%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.com%2Fisrael-news%2F2023-04-28%2Fty-article-magazine%2F.highlight%2Fweapons-training-and-cash-israel-bribed-liberian-officials-for-years-cables-reveal%2F00000187-c368-d554-a5b7-df6c62ae0000%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHaaretz%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reveal%20how%20Israel%20paid%20bribes%20to%20diplomats%2C%20members%20of%20the%20military%20junta%20in%20Liberia%2C%20and%20its%20dictator%20Samuel%20Doe%20in%20exchange%20for%20the%20renewal%20of%20relations%20with%20Israel%20and%20to%20vote%20in%20its%20favour%20at%20the%20United%20Nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20the%20renewal%20of%20diplomatic%20and%20security%20relations%20with%20Liberia%20in%201983%2C%20the%20activity%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20private%20companies%20in%20Liberia%20was%20renewed%2C%20with%20the%20assistance%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20ministry.%20One%20of%20the%20key%20businessmen%20was%20Mordechai%20Yona.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27162222%2F21%25C2%25BA_President_of_Liberia_Samuel_Doe.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22200%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665466%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22242%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESamuel%20Doe.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%2FBobanchi%2FCC%20BY-SA%204.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20on%20April%2019%2C%201996%2C%20Ronan%20Bergman%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EHaaretz%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20details%20about%20the%20dramatic%20rescue%20of%20the%20employees%20and%20property%20of%20Yona%E2%80%99s%20company%20after%20the%20Doe%20regime%20collapsed%2C%20in%20which%20Doe%20himself%20was%20executed.%20Dozens%20of%20telegrams%20recently%20disclosed%20to%20the%20public%20%E2%80%93%20available%20with%20the%20Israel%20State%20Archives%20%E2%80%93%20reveal%20Yona%E2%80%99s%20problematic%20business%20conduct%20in%20Liberia%20with%20the%20assistance%20and%20full%20knowledge%20of%20Israeli%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98You%20wonder%20where%20the%20funding%20came%20from%3F%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20help%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20ministry%2C%20Yona%20obtained%20permits%20to%20issue%20foreign%20currency%2C%20to%20transfer%20equipment%20out%20from%20Israel%2C%20for%20loans%20and%20financing%20for%20various%20projects%20in%20Liberia%2C%20including%20a%20contract%20for%20a%20period%20of%2037%20years%20for%20the%20exploitation%20and%20extensive%20logging%20of%20Liberia%E2%80%99s%20forests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20telegram%20dated%20March%204%2C%201985%2C%20sent%20by%20the%20Israeli%20ambassador%20in%20Liberia%E2%80%99s%20capital%2C%20Monrovia%2C%20Gabriel%20Gabrieli%2C%20it%20was%20written%20that%20the%20Israeli%20state%20had%20brought%20Yona%20to%20Liberia%20and%20his%20company%E2%80%99s%20projects%20are%20identified%20with%20that%20of%20Israel.%20In%20the%20Israeli%20newspaper%20%3Cem%3EDavar%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20it%20was%20reported%20on%20March%2011%2C%201985%2C%20that%20these%20projects%20were%20in%20the%20range%20of%20one%20billion%20US%20Dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2026%2C%201985%2C%20the%20foundation%20stone%20for%20the%20new%20ministry%20of%20defence%20building%20in%20Monrovia%3Cstrong%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewhich%20Yona%20undertook%20at%20the%20estimated%20cost%20of%2020%20million%20dollars%2C%20was%20laid.%20Four%20days%20earlier%2C%20Ambassador%20Gabrieli%20had%20sought%20the%20advice%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20Director%20of%20the%20Africa%20Department%20in%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs%2C%20Avi%20Premor%2C%20on%20what%20to%20do%20informing%20him%20that%20Yona%20demanded%20that%20he%20be%20allowed%20to%20speak%20at%20the%20foundation%20stone%20laying%20ceremony.%20Gabrieli%20also%20added%20that%20%E2%80%9Cconstructing%20a%20luxury%20building%20during%20the%20worst%20economic%20depression%20that%20has%20ever%20hit%20Liberia%20is%20unrealistic.%E2%80%9D%20Even%20worse%2C%20Gabrieli%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9COf%20course%2C%20you%20wonder%20where%20the%20funding%20came%20from%20and%20I%20have%20no%20idea%20about%20that.%E2%80%9D%20Gabrieli%20was%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20he%20should%20reject%20Yona%E2%80%99s%20demand%20since%20%E2%80%9Cit%20is%20impossible%20for%20the%20representative%20of%20Israel%20here%20to%20praise%20this%20ostentatious%20construction%20in%20front%20of%20a%20large%20audience%2C%20including%20TV%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETraining%20for%20the%20dictator%E2%80%99s%20army%20and%20diplomatic%20crises%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%201987%2C%20Israeli%20prime%20minister%20Yitzhak%20Shamir%20visited%20Liberia%20and%20met%20with%20Doe.%20According%20to%20a%20summary%20prepared%20by%20the%20then%20Israeli%20ambassador%20in%20Monrovia%2C%20Aryeh%20Ivtsen%2C%20on%20July%201%2C%201987%2C%20Doe%20complained%20to%20Shamir%20that%20Yona%20had%20received%20his%20%E2%80%9Cbig%20contract%20in%20Liberia%E2%80%9D%2C%20even%20though%20he%20had%20many%20competitors%20since%20he%20undertook%20a%20contract%20to%20supply%20vehicles%20to%20the%20army%20and%20the%20police%2C%20but%20provided%20only%2010%20jeeps%20in%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20telegrams%2C%20this%20trade-off%20was%20done%20because%20the%20Doe%20regime%20was%20bankrupt.%20Doe%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20freely%20purchase%20military%20equipment%20from%20the%20aid%20money%20he%20received%20from%20the%20US%20and%20other%20countries%20or%20from%20the%20World%20Bank%20loan%2C%20without%20their%20prior%20approval.%20According%20to%20a%20telegram%20sent%20on%20October%208%2C%201986%2C%20by%20Ambassador%20Ivtzen%2C%20Yona%20also%20purchased%20military%20equipment%20for%20the%20training%20with%20Israeli%20instructors%20of%20100%20recruits%20in%20the%20murderous%20anti-terrorist%20unit%20(SATU).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20Yona%20made%20false%20promises%20to%20Doe%20that%20resulted%20in%20a%20crisis%20between%20the%20countries.%20One%20of%20them%20was%20to%20establish%20a%20rice%20farm%20%E2%80%93%20one%20of%20the%20staple%20foods%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Liberia%20at%20that%20time.%20In%20a%20memorandum%20written%20by%20deputy%20director%20of%20the%20ministry%20of%20foreign%20affairs%2C%20Mordechai%20Drori%2C%20on%20October%202%2C%201984%2C%20it%20was%20written%20that%20Dr.%20Raanan%20Weitz%20(head%20of%20the%20Jewish%20Agency%E2%80%99s%20settlement%20department)%20called%20him%20and%20warned%2C%20%E2%80%9CMordechai%20Yona%20does%20not%20intend%20to%20realise%20the%20rice%20farm%20that%20is%20so%20important%20to%20Liberia%2C%20but%20hopes%20to%20get%20other%20projects%20that%20really%20interest%20him%E2%80%A6%20He%20estimates%20that%20Yona%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20financial%20resources%20for%20the%20farm%20and%20therefore%20warns%20us%20against%20political%20entanglement.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20entanglement%20did%20happen%20%E2%80%93%20the%20rice%20farm%20was%20never%20established.%20The%20Doe%20regime%20repeatedly%20accused%20the%20Israeli%20government%20of%20being%20responsible%20for%20the%20matter%20and%20the%20Liberian%20minister%20of%20agriculture%20even%20threatened%20to%20sever%20relations%20with%20Israel.%20The%20Israeli%20foreign%20ministry%20tried%20unsuccessfully%20to%20find%20a%20solution.%20But%20in%20a%20telegram%20sent%20on%20July%2012%2C%201985%2C%20by%20Ilan%20Hartov%20from%20the%20Economic%20Department%20at%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs%20to%20the%20deputy%20ambassador%20in%20Monrovia%20Yaffa%20Ben%20Ari%2C%20he%20wrote%20the%20obvious%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20many%20meetings%20in%20the%20ministry%20on%20this%20matter.%20I%20think%20there%20is%20a%20consensus%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20that%20is%2C%20we%20are%20unable%20to%20grow%20rice%20in%20Liberia%20and%20the%20Liberians%20should%20be%20removed%20from%20the%20issue%20%E2%80%A6%20No%20rice%20is%20grown%20in%20Israel.%20There%20are%20no%20rice%20growing%20experts%20in%20Israel.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20telegram%20sent%20on%20August%2013%2C%201985%2C%20by%20Deputy%20Ambassador%20Yaffa%20Ben%20Ari%20to%20the%20Director%20of%20the%20Africa%20Department%20at%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs%2C%20Avi%20Primor%2C%20she%20reported%20on%20the%20concerns%20of%20the%20Israeli%20Embassy%20in%20Monrovia%2C%20in%20light%20of%20the%20information%20that%20Yona%20had%20not%20paid%20debts%20to%20suppliers%2C%20salaries%20to%20workers%2C%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20labor%20disputes%20had%20arisen%20at%20his%20projects%20in%20Liberia.%20Ben%20Ari%20warned%20that%20%E2%80%9CMordechai%20Yona%20began%20to%20operate%20in%20Liberia%20with%20the%20encouragement%20of%20the%20Israeli%20government%20and%20with%20our%20assistance.%20His%20failure%20will%20be%20our%20failure.%20In%20the%20sensitive%20state%20of%20relations%20with%20the%20Liberians%2C%20such%20an%20%E2%80%98explosion%E2%80%99%20could%20have%20very%20serious%20consequences.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20solution%20of%20sorts%2C%20on%20October%2018%2C%201985%2C%20the%20then%20foreign%20minister%20Yitzhak%20Shamir%20personally%20recommended%20to%20the%20Bank%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20Foreign%20Investment%20Committee%20to%20approve%20a%20guarantee%20from%20the%20assets%20of%20Yona%E2%80%99s%20companies%20in%20Israel%20for%20a%20bridging%20loan%20of%20%242%20million%20for%20the%20deforestation%20project%20in%20Liberia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMixing%20private%20and%20state%20interests%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20described%20above%20is%20not%20unique%20to%20Liberia%2C%20but%20stems%20from%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20relations%20system.%20The%20US%20and%20the%20countries%20of%20Western%20Europe%20provide%20huge%20amounts%20of%20financial%20aid%20for%20the%20security%20and%20civilian%20needs%20of%20countries%20that%20have%20interests%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20in%20contrast%2C%20Israel%20does%20not%20usually%20provide%20financial%20aid%2C%20and%20the%20countries%20are%20supposed%20to%20finance%20the%20Israeli%20projects%20and%20services%20themselves.%20This%20is%20due%20to%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20limited%20budget%20and%20its%20reluctance%20to%20set%20a%20precedent.%20Israel%20is%20afraid%20that%20countries%20will%20demand%20and%20%E2%80%98extort%E2%80%99%20funds%20from%20it%20as%20a%20condition%20for%20the%20establishment%20and%20expansion%20of%20its%20relations%20with%20them%2C%20or%20that%20they%20will%20threaten%20to%20sever%20relations%20if%20they%20do%20not%20receive%20the%20financial%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20substitute%20for%20financial%20aid%2C%20the%20Israeli%20Ministry%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs%20usually%20presents%20the%20activities%20of%20private%20Israeli%20companies%20as%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20official%20aid%20of%20the%20Israeli%20government.%20Thus%2C%20in%20a%20telegram%20sent%20by%20Rafi%20Gamzo%20from%20the%20Economic%20Department%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs%20on%20June%207%2C%201987%2C%20he%20wrote%20that%20due%20to%20the%20serious%20financial%20situation%20of%20the%20Liberian%20government%2C%20it%20is%20proposed%20not%20to%20make%20promises%20from%20the%20Israeli%20government%20in%20the%20economic%20field%20%E2%80%9Cand%20to%20be%20content%20with%20encouraging%20and%20assisting%20the%20operations%20of%20Yona%E2%80%99s%20company%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGamzo%20explained%20that%20the%20realisation%20and%20success%20of%20Yona%E2%80%99s%20projects%20%E2%80%9Cwith%20the%20backing%20of%20the%20Israeli%20government%2C%20will%20show%20that%2C%20even%20if%20late%2C%20Israel%20lives%20up%20to%20its%20promises.%E2%80%9D%20In%20this%20way%2C%20a%20situation%20is%20created%20where%2C%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20regimes%20in%20these%20countries%2C%20the%20State%20of%20Israel%20is%20responsible%20for%20the%20failures%20and%20successes%20of%20the%20Israeli%20private%20companies%20that%20operate%20in%20them%2C%20and%20the%20representatives%20of%20the%20Israeli%20Foreign%20Ministry%20become%20a%20kind%20of%20babysitters%20for%20Israeli%20businessmen%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20described%20is%20not%20unique%20to%20Yona.%20Many%20businessmen%20and%20large%20companies%20in%20the%20Israeli%20economy%20operate%20abroad%20with%20the%20assistance%20and%20coordination%20of%20the%20Ministries%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs%20and%20Defense.%20The%20personal%20interests%20of%20the%20businessmen%20and%20private%20companies%20are%20mixed%20with%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20State%20of%20Israel%2C%20which%20actually%20becomes%20responsible%20for%20their%20financial%20stability%20and%20is%20sometimes%20required%20to%20help%20cover%20up%20the%20problems%20in%20their%20conduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20the%20mixing%20of%20personal%20and%20state%20interests%20is%20done%20in%20the%20dark%20and%20hidden%20from%20the%20public%20in%20Israel.%20Until%20this%20method%20is%20stopped%2C%20there%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20many%20more%20corruption%20cases%20of%20Israeli%20public%20officials%20and%20private%20businessmen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20Israeli%20media%20and%20public%20are%20indifferent%20to%20the%20involvement%20of%20the%20Israeli%20governments%20and%20private%20Israeli%20companies%20in%20dubious%20projects%2C%20corruption%2C%20and%20human%20rights%20violations%20in%20distant%20countries%20%E2%80%93%20often%20with%20the%20racist%20excuse%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthat%E2%80%99s%20how%20things%20work%E2%80%9D%20in%20Africa%2C%20Latin%20America%2C%20Southeast%20Asia%20or%20Eastern%20Europe.%20But%20it%20may%20come%20back%20as%20a%20boomerang%20to%20those%20indifferent%2C%20as%20happened%20when%20Yona%E2%80%99s%20company%20collapsed%20in%20Israel%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.the7eye.org.il%2F492540%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0first%20appeared%20on%20the%20Hebrew%20media%20platform%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.the7eye.org.il%2Fabout%2Fenglish%5C%22%3EThe%20Seventh%20Eye%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690457437000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27161559%2FHutz.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fleaked-diplomatic-cables-reveal-shady-nexus-between-israel-foreign-ministry-and-private-firms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20state%20of%20Israel%20paid%20bribes%20to%20diplomats%2C%20members%20of%20the%20military%20junta%20in%20Liberia%2C%20and%20its%20dictator%20Samuel%20Doe%20to%20aid%20the%20growth%20of%20Mordechai%20Yona's%20Heftziba%20company%2C%20leaked%20diplomatic%20cables%20revealed%20recently.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fleaked-diplomatic-cables-reveal-shady-nexus-between-israel-foreign-ministry-and-private-firms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20intoxicated%20United%20Airlines%20pilot%2C%20who%20turned%20up%20for%20a%20transatlantic%20flight%20'staggering'%20and%20with%20'glassy'%20eyes%2C%20was%20given%20a%206-month%20suspended%20prison%20sentence%2C%20report%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223242%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20United%20Airlines%20plane%20flying%20in%20a%20clear%20blue%20sky%20with%20its%20landing%20gear%20down.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b4009b9751e300192a4164%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222424%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20United%20Airlines%20plane.%3Cp%3EThi