n%20the%201950s.%20The%20main%20faction%20of%20the%20National%20Socialist%20Council%20of%20Nagaland%2C%20the%20biggest%20Naga%20insurgency%2C%20struck%20a%20ceasefire%20agreement%20with%20the%20federal%20government%20in%201997%2C%20and%20is%20still%20in%C2%A0talks%20with%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3EThe%20Meitei%20groups%2C%20which%20appeared%20soon%20after%20the%20Naga%20militant%20outfits%2C%20have%20not%20entered%20into%20peace%20discussions%2C%20though%20they%20are%20much%20less%20active%20than%20in%20the%20past.%20The%20security%20forces%20refer%20to%20them%20as%20%E2%80%9Cvalley-based%20insurgent%20groups%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kuki%20militant%20groups%20emerged%20only%20in%20the%20early%201990s%2C%20as%20a%20response%20to%20Naga%20attacks%2C%20but%20they%20signed%20a%20tripartite%20Suspension%20of%20Operations%20agreement%20with%20the%20federal%20and%20state%20governments%20in%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3ESince%20then%2C%20the%20Kuki%20militants%3Cb%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3Ehave%20been%20confined%20to%20thirteen%20camps%2C%20with%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3Etheir%20arms%20under%20lock%20and%20key.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3EBut%20the%20two%20Kuki%20umbrella%20militant%20groups%20that%20signed%20the%20agreement%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3E%2C%20the%20Kuki%20National%20Organisation%20and%20the%20United%20People%E2%80%99s%20Front%2C%20had%20to%20wait%20until%202017%20for%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3ENew%20Delhi%20to%20start%20actual%20peace%20talks.%20During%20these%20talks%2C%20the%20Kuki%20demanded%20the%20creation%20of%20territorial%20councils%20that%20would%20grant%20more%20autonomy%20to%20tribal%20communities%20in%20Manipur.%C2%A0Negotiations%20are%20proceeding%20slowly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%2