he%20remaining%2035%25%20of%20the%20vote%20of%20non-Yadav%20OBC%20voters%20who%20have%20shifted%20to%20the%20BJP%20since%20the%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20father%20and%20SP%20founder%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20had%20worked%20diligently%20to%20win%20over%20a%20large%20number%20of%20non-Yadav%20OBC%20voters%20by%20building%20up%20leaders%20like%20Beni%20Prasad%20Verma%2C%20Phoolan%20Devi%20and%20Raghuraj%20Shakya%2C%20among%20others.%20However%2C%20Akhilesh%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20carry%20forward%20that%20legacy%20effectively%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20decline%20in%20the%20SP%E2%80%99s%20non-Yadav%20OBC%20vote%20bank.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20preparation%20for%20the%202022%20assembly%20elections%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20did%20form%20alliances%20with%20various%20regional%20outfits%20representing%20these%20castes%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20significant%20increase%20in%20the%20SP%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Evote%20share%20from%2021%25%20in%202017%20to%2035%25%20in%202022.%C2%A0But%20this%20failed%20to%20pay%20the%20desired%20dividends.%20However%2C%20now%20the%20challenge%20he%20faces%20is%20in%20maintaining%20the%20unity%20of%20the%20coalition%20of%20small%20parties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERaj%20Pal%20Kashyap%2C%20state%20president%20of%20SP%E2%80%99s%20Backward%20Cell%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20already%20commenced%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eyatras%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(rallies)%20for%20the%20OBC%E2%80%99s%20and%20have%20conducted%20seminars%20on%20caste%20census%20and%20are%20conducting%204%20programs%20every%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27131658%2Funnamed-3.jp