.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27131611%2Funnamed-1-1.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27131611%2Funnamed-1-1-300x217.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665412%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22742%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EOm%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%20with%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40oprajbhar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%202017%20assembly%20elections%2C%20Om%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%20was%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20NDA%20and%20also%20became%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20government.%20However%2C%20a%20political%20opportunist%20that%20he%20is%2C%20he%20switched%20loyalties%20to%20the%20SP%20just%20before%20the%202022%20state%20assembly%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20significance%20can%20be%20gauged%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20sent%20him%20a%20congratulatory%20message%20on%20the%C2%A0wedding%20of%20his%20son%20in%20June%20last%20year.%20The%20message%20came%20in%20handy%20for%20Rajbhar%20to%20claim%20his%20clout%20over%20the%20ruling%20dispensation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20Raj%20Pal%20Kashyap%20believes%20that%20Om%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%20leaving%20the%20SP%20alliance%20will%20not%20have%20a%20substantial%20impact.%20He%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COm%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%E2%80%99s%20absence%20will%20not%20harm%20us.%20We%20have%20influential%20Rajbhar%20leaders%20within%20our%20own%20ranks%2C%20such%20as%20Ram%20Achal%20Rajbhar%20and%20Sukhdeo%20Rajbhar%E2%80%99s%20son.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhat-does-om-prakash-rajbhars-return-to-nda-mean-for-up-politics%5C%22%3EWhat%20Does%20Om%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%E2%80%99s%20Return%20to%20NDA%20Mean%20for%20UP%20Politics%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKurmi%20vote%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKurmi%20voters%20are%20estimated%20to%20constitute%20around%205%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population.%20Significantly%2C%20about%2015%25%20of%20these%20are%20concentrated%20in%20Eastern%20UP.%20According%20to%20the%20post-poll%20study%20conducted%20by%20CSDS%2C%20NDA%20received%2066%25%20of%20Kurmi%20and%20Koeri%20votes%20in%20the%202022%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20UP%2C%20Sone%20Lal%20Patel%20was%20an%20influential%20Kurmi%20leader%20who%20formed%20his%20own%20party.%20However%2C%20after%20his%20demise%2C%20his%20party%20split%20into%20two%20factions%20%E2%80%93%20one%20under%20Sone%20Lal%20Patel%E2%80%99s%20daughter%20Anupriya%20Patel%20which%20is%20allied%20with%20BJP%3B%20and%20the%20Apna%20Dal%20(Kamerawadi)%20led%20by%20Sonelal%20Patel%E2%80%99s%20other%20daughter%20Pallavi%20Patel%2C%20allied%20with%20the%20SP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27132026%2Funnamed-2-1.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27132026%2Funnamed-2-1.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27132026%2Funnamed-2-1-300x194.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27132026%2Funnamed-2-1-1024x660.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665414%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22774%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAkhilesh%20Yadav%20with%20Krishna%20Patel%20paying%20tribute%20to%20Sone%20Lal%20Patel%20on%20his%20birth%20anniversary.%20Photo%3A%20SP%20Office%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESP%20allocated%20six%20seats%20to%20the%20Apna%20Dal(K)%20for%20the%202022%20assembly%20elections.%20Pallavi%20Patel%20contested%20on%20the%20SP%20ticket%20and%20defeated%20Keshav%20Prasad%20Maurya%2C%20who%20currently%20serves%20as%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20in%20the%20Adityanath%20government.%20But%20Apna%20Dal(K)%20could%20not%20win%20even%20a%20single%20seat%20and%20got%20only%200.278%25%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Evotes.%C2%A0On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20NDA%E2%80%99s%20ally%20Apna%20Dal%20(S)%20contested%20the%20assembly%20elections%20on%2017%20seats%20and%20won%2012%20of%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESenior%20journalist%20Sharat%20Pradhan%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSP%20lacks%20prominent%20Kurmi%20leaders.%20Despite%20Pallavi%20Patel%E2%80%99s%20significant%20victory%20against%20Keshav%20Maurya%2C%20Akhilesh%20does%20not%20appear%20to%20be%20giving%20her%20much%20importance.%20In%20sharp%20contrast%2C%20the%20BJP%20seems%20to%20recognize%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20Kurmi%20vote%20and%20has%20therefore%20given%20Anupriya%20Patel%20a%20berth%20in%20the%20Modi%20government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20significance%20of%20the%20Kurmi%20community%20can%20be%20observed%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20during%20this%20recent%20UP%20visit%20on%20July%207%2C%20Modi%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20visit%20the%20home%20of%20Pankaj%20Choudhary%2C%20a%20prominent%20Kurmi%20leader%20who%20is%20a%20six-time%20MP%20from%20Maharajganj.%20Currently%2C%20he%20is%20serving%20as%20a%20MoS%20in%20the%20central%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMaurya%2C%20Kushwaha%20and%20Shakya%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Maurya%2C%20Kushwaha%20and%20Shakya%20communities%20constitute%20around%206%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population.%20According%20to%20the%20CSDS%20post-poll%20study%2C%20the%20BJP%20received%2064%25%20of%20the%20votes%20from%20these%20communities%2C%20while%20the%20SP%20could%20obtain%20only%2022%25%20in%20the%202022%20assembly%20elections.%20Political%20analysts%20suggest%20that%20it%20seems%20difficult%20for%20SP%20to%20recapture%20this%20vote%20bank%20from%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20a%20view%20to%20wooing%20these%20communities%20in%20the%202022%20assembly%20elections%2C%20Akhilesh%20adopted%20a%20two-fold%20strategy.%20Firstly%2C%20he%20struck%20an%20alliance%20with%20Keshav%20Dev%20Maurya%20who%20runs%20a%20regional%20outfit%20called%20Mahan%20Dal.%20But%20this%20time%20Keshav%20Dev%20has%20already%20declared%20his%20unconditional%20support%20to%20Mayawati%E2%80%99s%20BSP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAkhilesh%E2%80%99s%20second%20strategy%20was%20to%20bring%20veteran%20Maurya%20community%20leader%20Swami%20Prasad%20Maurya%20into%20SP%2C%20who%20joined%20the%20party%20just%20before%20the%202022%20assembly%20elections.%20Maurya%20however%20created%20much%20embarrassment%20for%20Akhilesh%20by%20making%20certain%20controversial%20remarks%20about%20%3Cem%3ERamcharitmanas%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESenior%20journalist%20Brijesh%20Shukla%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CSwami%20Prasad%20Maurya%E2%80%99s%20lost%20his%20own%20seat%20in%20Kushinagar%2C%20his%20influence%20is%20limited.%20His%20recent%20statements%20concerning%20the%20Ramcharitmanas%20are%20causing%20more%20harm%20than%20good%20for%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EJat%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20SP%20faces%20a%20significant%20challenge%20in%20the%20Jat-dominated%20Western%20UP.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20difficult%20for%20SP%20to%20perform%20well%20independently%20in%20the%20region%20due%20to%20the%20limited%20presence%20of%20Yadav%20voters.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%202022%20assembly%20elections%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20played%20his%20cards%20well%20by%20aligning%20with%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%E2%80%99s%20(RLD)%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%2C%20the%20grandson%20of%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%2C%20who%20has%20been%20among%20the%20tallest%20Jat%20leaders%20from%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20Jat%20vote%20dropped%20from%2057%25%20in%20the%202017%20assembly%20elections%20to%2033%25%20in%20the%202022%20elections%20after%20SP%E2%80%99s%20alliance%2C%20according%20to%20CSDS%20post-poll%20study.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERam%20Dutt%20Tripathi%2C%20a%20former%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBBC%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0correspondent%2C%20says%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9C2022%20election%20was%20a%20significant%20opportunity%20for%20Akhilesh%20and%20Jayant%20to%20attract%20the%20Jat%20votes%2C%20especially%20given%20the%20large-scale%20farmers%E2%80%99%20movement%20in%20Western%20UP%20and%20the%20sympathy%20factor%20for%20Jayant%20among%20the%20Jats%20due%20to%20his%20father%20Ajit%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20demise.%20Despite%20the%20circumstances%2C%20if%20the%20Jats%20did%20not%20vote%20for%20the%20SP%20alliance%2C%20it%20seems%20very%20difficult%20for%20the%20Jats%20to%20come%20back%20to%20the%20SP%20fold.%E2%80%9D%20Meanwhile%2C%20speculation%20is%20rife%20that%20the%20BJP%20may%20succeed%20in%20its%20subtle%20moves%20to%20woo%20Jayant%20Chaudhary.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3EPDA%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98D%E2%80%99%20stands%20for%20Dalit%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EComing%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98D%E2%80%99%20of%20Akhilesh%E2%80%99s%20PDA%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20has%C2%A022%25%20Dalit%20voters.%20The%20SP%20is%20also%20focusing%20on%20securing%20their%20support.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20party%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20asset%20is%20R.K.%20Choudhary%2C%20a%20veteran%20Dalit%20leader%20and%20former%20associate%20of%20BSP%20founder%20Kanshiram.%20He%20is%20visiting%20Dalit-dominated%20villages%20to%20spread%20the%20word%20that%20SP%20is%20the%20true%20well-wisher%20of%20Dalits.%20He%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20raising%20concerns%20related%20to%20caste-based%20reservations%2C%20social%20justice%20and%20equality.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27132210%2Funnamed-3-2.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27132210%2Funnamed-3-2.png%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27132210%2Funnamed-3-2-300x225.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27132210%2Funnamed-3-2-1024x768.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665418%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22864%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERK%20Choudhary%20addressing%20a%20gathering%20in%20Hardoi.%20Photo%3A%20RK%20Choudhary%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESP%20witnessed%20a%20slight%20increase%20in%20the%20Dalit%20vote%20share%20in%20the%202022%20assembly%20elections.%20The%20Jatav%20votes%20increased%20by%206%25%2C%20while%20non-Jatav%20votes%20increased%20by%2012%25.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20Akhilesh%20faces%20three%20significant%20challenges%20in%20securing%20the%20Dalit%20vote.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirstly%2C%20the%20sympathy%20factor%20for%20Mayawati%20among%20Jatavs.%20Ramraj%2C%20a%20grocery%20store%20owner%20in%20Banda%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Jatav%20community%20carries%20a%20significant%20sense%20of%20remorse%20and%20deep%20concern%20for%20Mayawati.%20In%20the%20forthcoming%20election%2C%20even%20those%20Jatavs%20who%20had%20previously%20parted%20ways%20with%20the%20BSP%20are%20returning%2C%20while%20the%20existing%20supporters%20are%20steadfastly%20standing%20alongside%20Behenji.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESecondly%2C%20the%20threat%20SP%20is%20facing%20is%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20success%20at%20capturing%20a%20good%20chunk%20of%20non-Jatav%20Dalits%20since%20the%202014%20elections%20and%20its%20bid%20to%20increase%20its%20vote%20share%20among%20Jatavs%20as%20well.%20Asim%20Arun%20former%20police%20commissioner%20of%20Kanpur%20and%20now%20minister%20of%20social%20welfare%20in%20the%20UP%20government%20says%2C%C2%A0%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20continuously%20working%20among%20the%20Dalits%2C%20and%20giving%20them%20leadership%20positions%20in%20the%20party.%20Moreover%2C%20our%20welfare%20schemes%20like%20the%20free%20housing%20scheme%2C%20ration%20and%20construction%20of%20toilets%20have%20consolidated%20their%20support%20for%20BJP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThirdly%2C%20there%20is%20a%20longstanding%20conflict%20between%20Jatavs%20and%20Yadavs%20in%20the%20villages%2C%20which%20has%20led%20to%20Jatavs%20not%20aligning%20with%20the%20SP.%20However%2C%20Chandra%20Shekhar%20Choudhary%2C%20the%20state%20chief%20of%20SP%E2%80%99s%20Ambedkar%20Vahini%20argues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20fight%20for%20power%20is%20no%20longer%20between%20different%20factions%20of%20PDA%20but%20rather%20against%20the%20NDA.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPDA%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98A%E2%80%99%20means%20alpasankhyak%20(minority)%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EComing%20to%20alpsankhyaks%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20is%20relying%20heavily%20on%20the%20support%20of%20the%20minority%20community%20which%20has%20been%20a%20core%20base%20of%20the%20party%20ever%20since%20its%20inception.%20In%20UP%2C%20there%20are%20approximately%2019%25%20Muslim%20voters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20a%20post-poll%20study%20by%20Axis%20My%20India%2C%2082%25%20of%20Muslims%20voted%20for%20the%20SP%20alliance%20in%20the%202022%20assembly%20elections%2C%20even%20surpassing%20the%20Muslim%20vote%20share%20the%20SP-BSP-RLD%20alliance%20received%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0However%2C%20this%20vote%20bank%20is%20now%20facing%20threats%20as%20the%20BSP%20and%20All%20India%20Majlis-e-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%20(AIMIM)%20performed%20well%20in%20some%20places%20in%20the%20recent%20civic%20elections%20held%20in%20May%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESP%20spokesperson%20Abbas%20Haider%20asserts%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20significant%20difference%20between%20civic%20elections%20and%20Lok%20Sabha.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20there%20is%20an%20election%20to%20change%20the%20government%20at%20the%20national%20level%2C%20the%20entire%20Muslim%20community%20will%20stand%20unitedly%20with%20Akhilesh%20Yadav.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27132324%2Funnamed-4-1.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27132324%2Funnamed-4-1.png%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27132324%2Funnamed-4-1-300x300.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27132324%2Funnamed-4-1-1024x1024.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27132324%2Funnamed-4-1-150x150.png%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665419%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221153%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAbbas%20Haider%20with%20supporters%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2FAbbas%20Haider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBSP%20does%20present%20a%20notable%20challenge%20to%20the%20Muslim%20vote%20bank%20of%20