ought%20Too%20Little%20or%20Too%20Much%20Rain%20All%20at%20Once%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27132337%2FF1ZRf3zWIAEpsab.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20monsoon%20season%20of%202023%20has%20so%20far%20brought%20either%20too%20little%20or%20too%20much%20rain%20all%20at%20once.%20Seven%20weeks%20into%20the%20season%2C%20some%20regions%20have%20experienced%20previously%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Ftorrential-rain-floods-kill-22-across-northern-india-2023-07-10%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20missing%20rains%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20normalizing%20the%20overall%20rain%20tally%20in%20some%20places%20but%20also%20causing%20destruction%2C%20deaths%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Ftopics%2F4868%2Fagricultural-sector-in-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edamage%20to%20crops%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20rice.%20The%20fallout%20went%20so%20far%20that%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Fchart%2F30491%2Fbiggest-rice-exporters%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Indian%20government%20on%20Thursday%3C%2Fa%3E%20issued%20an%20export%20ban%20on%20non-Basmati%20white%20rice%2C%20saying%20it%20had%20to%20curb%20rising%20domestic%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20many%20Indian%20states%20are%20still%20showing%20a%20rain%20deficit%20seven%20weeks%20into%20the%20monsoon%20season.%20But%20even%20in%20states%20with%20a%20rain%20tally%20that%20can%20be%20considered%20normal%20at%20this%20point%2C%20weeks%20of%20no%20rain%20alternating%20with%20heavy%20downpour%20can%20take%20its%20toll%20on%20crops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20map%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmausam.imd.gov.in%2Fimd_latest%2Fcontents%2Fweek_ra