20of%20gear%20in%20the%20state%2C%20with%20water%20bodies%20across%20the%20state%20swollen%20and%20roads%20inundated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fincessant-rains-batter-telangana-red-alert-issued%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IMF%20Chief%20Economist%20Urges%20Reversal%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Restriction%20on%20Rice%20Exports%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27113206%2FFySTIY3WIAICKM3.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Chief%20economist%20at%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20(IMF)%20Pierre-Olivier%20Gourinchas%20on%20Tuesday%20(July%2025)%20said%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20restriction%20on%20exports%20of%20non-basmati%20rice%20could%20exacerbate%20global%20food%20price%20inflation%20and%20should%20be%20reversed%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-s-rice-restrictions-could-fuel-food-price-inflation-imf-economist-123072500863_1.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGourinchas%2C%20while%20addressing%20a%20news%20conference%2C%20said%20that%20the%20move%20would%20have%20a%20similar%20effect%20to%20the%20suspension%20of%20Ukraine%20Black%20Sea%20grain%20export%20deal%20and%20drive%20up%20grain%20prices%20in%20other%20countries%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20could%20rise%20by%2010-15%25%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20current%20environment%2C%20these%20types%20of%20restrictions%20are%20likely%20to%20exacerbate%20volatility%20on%20food%20prices%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%2C%20and%20they%20can%20also%20lead%20to%20retaliatory%20measures.%20We%20would%20encourage%20the%20removal%20of%20these%20types%20of%20export%20restrictions%20because%20they%20can%20be%20harmful%20globally%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20Gourinchas%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20had%20banned%20the%20export%20of%20non-basmati%20rice%20last%20week%20owing%20to%20fears%20of%20a%20domestic%20shortage%20after%20late%20monsoon%20rains%20hurt%20paddy%20crops%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fhow-to%2Fwhy-indian-rice-export-ban-is-so-important-to-global-trade%2Farticleshow%2F102015630.cms%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2020%2C%20the%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifpri.org%2Fblog%2Findias-new-ban-rice-exports-potential-threats-global-supply-prices-and-food-security%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20would%20restrict%20exports%20of%20non-basmati%20rice%20to%20calm%20domestic%20rice%20prices%20that%20had%20risen%20more%20than%2030%25%20since%20October%202022.%20The%20ban%20would%20halt%20overseas%20sales%20of%20the%20grain%20with%20%E2%80%9Cimmediate%20effect%E2%80%9D%20and%20is%20estimated%20to%20cover%20about%2075%25-80%25%20of%20Indian%20rice%20exports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20accounts%20for%20more%20than%2040%25%20of%20world%E2%80%99s%20rice%20exports%2C%20which%20amounted%20to%2055.4%20million%20metric%20tons%20in%202022.%20It%20shipped%20more%20rice%20than%20the%20combined%20shipment%20of%20the%20four%20next%20biggest%20exporters%20%E2%80%93%20Thailand%2C%20Vietnam%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20the%20United%20States%20%E2%80%93%20last%20year%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKey%20buyers%20of%20Indian%20non-basmati%20rice%20include%3A%20Benin%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20Angola%2C%20Cameroon%2C%20Djibouti%2C%20Guinea%2C%20Ivory%20Coast%2C%20Kenya%20and%20Nepal.%20Iran%2C%20Iraq%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20mainly%20buy%20premium%20basmati%20rice%20from%20India%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20restrictions%20on%20rice%20export%20came%20into