ching%20with%20our%20teachers%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Lori.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20quite%20a%20success%2C%20and%20we%20still%20have%20volunteers%20coming%20in%20from%20different%20countries%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20The%20school%20currently%20has%2013%20teachers%2C%20and%20the%20school%20is%20registered%20with%20the%20state%20education%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnother%20important%20aspect%20that%20we%20are%20very%20particular%20about%20is%20that%20all%20the%20learning%20takes%20place%20in%20the%20classrooms%20itself.%20Since%20the%20children%20here%20come%20from%20rural%20backgrounds%2C%20they%20do%20not%20have%20anyone%20back%20home%20to%20assist%20them.%20So%20we%20ensure%20that%20the%20children%20absorb%20all%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20learnt%20right%20here%20with%20us%20at%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20management%20of%20the%20school%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CPrior%20to%20the%20pandemic%2C%20we%20hosted%20travellers%20in%20the%20village%2C%20planned%20activities%20around%20the%20place%2C%20etc%2C%20and%20used%20those%20proceeds%20to%20run%20the%20school.%20However%2C%20when%20the%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20we%20could%20not%20proceed%20with%20this%20setup%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKunwar%2C%20who%20always%20loved%20her%20baking%20skills%2C%20suggested%20they%20open%20a%20bakery%20and%20cafe%20to%20raise%20funds.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20how%20the%20cafe%20came%20into%20existence%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Lori.%20%E2%80%9CI%20love%20baking%20and%20this%20seemed%20like%20the%20perfect%20idea.%20It%20serves%20as%20a%20great%20source%20of%20income%20for%20the%20school%20today.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCj7f9-Us0yV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3