her%20disabilities%20really%20became%20apparent.%20For%20us%2C%20she%20was%20just%20Moy%20Moy%2C%20this%20great%2C%20funny%2C%20little%20child.%20But%20when%20she%20started%20going%20to%20school%2C%20it%20was%20as%20if%20they%20put%20a%20spotlight%20on%20her%20difficulties.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20we%20realised%20this%20school%20system%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20right%20for%20Moy%20Moy.%20Everything%20at%20the%20Foundation%20has%20evolved%20from%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20put%20in%20place%20many%20provisions%20in%20the%20form%20of%20laws%20and%20policies%20for%20people%20with%20disabilities%2C%20but%20the%20implementation%20remains%20questionable.%20%3Cem%3EOutlook%20India%20%3C%2Fem%3Enoted%20that%20of%20the%2078.64%20lakh%20children%20with%20disabilities%20in%20the%20country%2C%20three-fourths%20of%20those%20aged%20five%20don%E2%80%99t%20attend%20any%20educational%20institution.%20About%2012%25%20drop%20out%2C%20and%2027%25%20have%20never%20attended%20any%20educational%20institute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20UNICEF%20report%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20early%20years%20(0%20to%208%20years)%20are%20the%20most%20extraordinary%20period%20of%20growth%20and%20development%20in%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20lifetime.%20The%20foundations%20of%20all%20learning%20are%20laid%20during%20these%20years.%20Getting%20the%20foundations%20right%20carries%20huge%20future%20benefits%3A%20better%20learning%20in%20school%20and%20higher%20educational%20attainment%2C%20which%20results%20in%20major%20social%20and%20economic%20gains%20for%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20820px)%20100vw%2C%20820px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Finclusive-education-1690291697.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22820%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22inclusive%20education%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Finclusive-education-1690291697.jpg%20820w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Finclusive-education-1690291697-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Finclusive-education-1690291697-500x282.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Finclusive-education-1690291697-768x433.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Finclusive-education-1690291697-150x85.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325144%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22462%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EUNICEF%20reports%20that%20the%20early%20years%20are%20the%20most%20extraordinary%20period%20of%20growth%20and%20development%20in%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20lifetime%3B%20Photo%3A%20Representational%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202020%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F234151%2Fnew-education-policy-2020-pdf-hrd-ministry-play-school-classes-vocational-coding-bagless-information-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Education%20Policy%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20laid%20great%20emphasis%20on%20inclusion%20in%20education%20that%20takes%20into%20consideration%20local%20contexts%20and%20diversity.%20The%20framework%20asserts%20that%20quality%20in%20the%20early%20childhood%20care%20ecosystem%20(ECCE)%20is%20the%20highest%20priority%2C%20as%20is%20the%20inclusion%20and%20equal%20participation%20of%20children%20with%20disabilities%20and%20those%20from%20economically%20disadvantaged%20groups.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20how%20do%20we%20extend%20the%20same%20future%20benefits%20to%20children%20with%20disabilities%2C%20who%20are%20disproportionately%20affected%20by%20an%20already%20fractured%20educational%20system%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20first%20programmes%20that%20the%20Foundation%20started%20was%20Karuna%20Vihar%2C%20an%20early%20childhood%20intervention%20centre%20that%20encourages%20the%20overall%20development%20of%20children%20between%20the%20ages%20of%200%20and%206%20by%20building%20on%20their%20strengths.%20Parents%20or%20guardians%20work%20closely%20with%20special%20educators%20and%20therapists%20so%20they%20can%20carry%20out%20the%20activities%20practised%20during%20lessons%20at%20home.%20They%20are%20also%20given%20counselling%20services%20and%20support%20group%20interventions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaruna%20Vihar%20also%20focuses%20on%20%E2%80%98play%E2%80%99%20including%20theatre%20and%20creative%20interventions%20like%20exercises%20to%20help%20develop%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20functional%20skills.%20They%20also%20involve%20play%20in%20developing%20individualised%20education%20plans%20for%20each%20child%20to%20learn%20speech%20and%20language%20skills%20and%20alternative%20communication%20systems%2C%20as%20well%20as%20encourage%20sensory%20stimulation%20and%20behaviour%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECrucial%20aspects%20of%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20life%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERupa%20Bishnoi%2C%20director%20of%20diversity%20and%20inclusion%20at%20LRF%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20talk%20about%20%E2%80%98inclusive%20education%E2%80%99%2C%20we%20also%20mean%20their%20inclusion%20in%20society.%20We%20have%20two%20catchwords%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%98participation%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98opportunity%E2%80%99.%20I%20specifically%20work%20for%20the%20mainstreaming%20of%20our%20children%20with%20the%20kids%2C%20the%20parents%2C%20and%20the%20schools.%20The%20last%20one%20has%20been%20the%20most%20negligent%20so%20far.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20commonplace%20in%20India%20for%20school%20managements%20to%20deny%20opportunities%20to%20children%20with%20disabilities%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20understanding%2C%20and%20sometimes%20due%20to%20an%20unwillingness%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctake%20responsibility%E2%80%9D.%20Children%20may%20also%20face%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F302809%2Fanoushka-jolly-shark-tank-started-kavach-an-app-for-bullying%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebullying%20and%20discrimination%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20these%20institutions%2C%20often%20with%20limited%20intervention%20by%20school%20authorities.%20Then%20there%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20accessible%20and%20safe%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20special%20educators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20work%20on%20a%20process%20where%20we%20contact%20schools%2C%20hold%20workshops%20with%20them%2C%20make%20them%20aware%20of%20different%20disabilities%2C%20establish%20relationships%E2%80%A6then%20we%20try%20to%20mainstream%20our%20children.%20For%20at%20least%20a%20year%20of%20support%2C%20we%20provide%20teachers%20with%20strategies%2C%20and%20work%20preventing%20the%20bullying%20of%20even%20parents%E2%80%A6This%20way%20we%E2%80%99ve%20managed%20to%20mainstream%20nine%20children%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCuXG-KtOEuJ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCuXG-KtOEuJ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCuXG-KtOEuJ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Latika%20Roy%20Foundation%20(%40latikaroyfoundation)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EInspired%20by%20Canada-based%20organisation%20CanChild%2C%20Rupa%20explains%20that%20LRF%20has%20also%20developed%20a%20Hindi%20version%20of%20a%20module%20titled%20%E2%80%98The%206%20F-Words%E2%80%99.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20are%20six%20functional%20areas%20for%20the%20inclusion%20of%20a%20child.%20These%20include%20Functioning%2C%20Family%2C%20Fitness%2C%20Friends%2C%20Fun%2C%20and%20Future.%20This%20covers%20very%20crucial%20aspects%20of%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20life.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJo%20notes%20that%20inclusion%20also%20goes%20beyond%20education%20in%20the%20sense%20that%20these%20children%20need%20camaraderie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20disabled%20people%2C%20opportunities%20to%20interact%20with%20peers%20are%20few%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20is%20common%20to%20loop%20or%20keep%20children%20with%20disabilities%20together%2C%20with%20minimal%20interactions%20with%20a%20wider%20circle.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20open%20up%20these%20areas%20so%20children%20with%20disabilities%20are%20more%20visible.%20That%E2%80%99s%20where%20our%20children%E2%80%99s%20club%20Latika%20Vihar%2C%20where%20these%20children%20interact%20and%20play%2C%20helps.%20It%E2%80%99s%20wonderful%20how%20they%20grow%20up%20together%2C%20the%20simple%20and%20uncomplicated%20way%20they%20interact%20with%20each%20other.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20child%20grows%2C%20integration%20and%20mainstreaming%20get%20tougher.%20%E2%80%9CChildren%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20these%20boundaries%20of%20disparity%2C%20class%2C%20caste%2C%20race%E2%80%A6.%E2%80%9D%20Rupa%20notes.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20neurotypical%20children%20too%2C%20in%20the%20early%20years%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20natural%20to%20have%20other%20children%20in%20the%20classroom%20who%20are%20different%20from%20them.%20Teachers%20are%20also%20more%20accepting%20of%20children%20of%20this%20age%3B%20there%E2%80%99s%20more%20benefit%20of%20the%20doubt.%20If%20we%20send%20a%20disabled%20kid%20to%20school%20without%20specifying%20that%20label%20or%20giving%20them%20that%20assessment%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20that%20teachers%20work%20very%20hard%20to%20make%20that%20child%20adjust.%20And%20then%20the%20child%20does%20beautifully.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmbracing%20the%20%E2%80%98difference%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJo%20opines%20that%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20education%20system%20is%20its%20rigidity.%20%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20an%20assumption%20that%20all%20children%20in%20the%20classroom%20learn%20the%20same%20way.%20We%20see%20how%20that%20fails%20so%20many%20kids%20who%20are%20already%20in%20school.%20When%20you%20bring%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296192%2Fshraddha-soparkar-provides-free-therapy-to-children-with-disabilities-madhuram-charitable-trust%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edisabled%20children%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20the%20mix%2C%20this%20becomes%20more%20apparent.%20The%20blame%20is%20put%20on%20the%20children%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20those%20with%20disabilities%2C%20but%20also%20those%20who%20have%20a%20different%20way%20of%20learning.%20We%20label%20them%20as%20%E2%80%98naughty%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98lazy%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98not%20interested%E2%80%99%E2%80%A6The%20system%20is%20designed%20in%20a%20way%20to%20exclude%20at%20multiple%20levels.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20a%20very%20academic%2C%20literal%20way%20of%20learning%2C%20when%20the%20fact%20is%20that%20children%20universally%20learn%20better%20by%20doing.%20This%20idea%20is%20not%20even%20well%20understood%2C%20let%20alone%20implemented.%20If%20we%20cater%20to%20this%20difference%20in%20ways%20of%20learning%2C%20we%20will%20automatically%20move%20towards%20more%20inclusivity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERupa%20emphasises%20on%20a%20social-emotional%20learning%20(SEL)%20curriculum.%20This%20is%20a%20process%20by%20which%20a%20child%20learns%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F285570%2Fchild-sexual-abuse-survivor-circles-of-safety-sexuality-education-school-curriculum%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunderstand%2C%20express%2C%20and%20manage%20emotions%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20is%20focused%20on%20helping%20them%20build%20healthy%20relationships%2C%20manage%20positive%20and%20negative%20feelings%2C%20and%20develop%20a%20sense%20of%20empathy%20and%20right%20or%20wrong.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20need%20to%20make%20each%20child%20feel%20significant%2C%20and%20have%20a%20sense%20of%20belonging%20in%20the%20classroom.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCrQjc7lORj2%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCrQjc7lORj2%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%