20refabricate%20(play%20elements%20like)%20a%20conventional%20merry%20go%20round.%20If%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20screw%20coming%20loose%2C%20you%20have%20to%20replace%20the%20merry%20go%20round%20entirely.%20Our%20playgrounds%20are%20like%20IKEA%20blocks.%20You%20can%20fix%20them%2C%20take%20them%20off%20when%20you%20want%20and%20put%20them%20in%20another%20place%20held%20together%20by%20nuts%20and%20bolts%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Rai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20facilitate%20play%20for%20young%20children%2C%20Anthill%20Creations%20has%20come%20up%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20innovations%20to%20facilitate%20greater%20inclusivity%20and%20work%20within%20the%20confines%20of%20different%20circumstances.%20For%20example%2C%20they%20came%20up%20with%20the%20concept%20of%20a%20Play%20Library.%20%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20we%20used%20smaller%20tires%20to%20create%20seating%20spaces%20in%20a%20more%20interesting%20way%20where%20the%20entire%20space%20felt%20very%20inviting%20for%20children%20to%20play.%20We%20had%20basically%20converted%20a%20library%20into%20a%20play%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Rai.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20one%20of%20Rai%E2%80%99s%20favourite%20innovations%20in%20recent%20years%20is%20this%20concept%20called%20%E2%80%98Playground%20on%20Wheels%E2%80%99%20which%20Anthill%20has%20developed.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20this%20idea%20honestly%20came%20when%20we%20were%20going%20around%20finding%20spaces%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20Bengaluru%20on%20where%20we%20can%20build%20these%20playgrounds%20for%20schools%20that%20contained%20three%20or%20four%20storeys%20and%20nothing%20else%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201514px)%20100vw%2C%201514px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FPlaygrounds-Anthill-123-1689861675.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221514%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Building%20innovative%20playground